<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="w-full min-h-[calc(100vh-76px)] bg-slate-100 py-10 px-4 md:px-12 box-border flex flex-col items-center print:bg-white print:py-0 print:px-0">
    <div class="w-full max-w-3xl flex justify-between items-center mb-6 print:hidden select-none">
        <a href="/my-room" class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 text-slate-700 font-bold px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs border border-slate-200 shadow-sm no-underline transition-all">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i><span>Back to My Room</span>
        </a>
        <button onClick="window.print()" class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs border-0 shadow-md cursor-pointer transition-all">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-print"></i><span>Print Lease Copy</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <!--Official Legal Document Sheet Layout Sheet Wrapper Container-->
    <div class="w-full max-w-3xl bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 box-border text-left text-slate-800 leading-relaxed font-serif text-base print:shadow-none print:border-none print:p-0">
        <div class="text-center space-y-1 mb-8 border-b-2 border-slate-800 pb-4">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight m-0 text-slate-900 uppercase">KASUNDUAN SA PAGPAPAUPA</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-widest m-0">Apartment Management System (AMS)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-sm">
            <p class="m-0 font-bold text-slate-900">SA PAGITAN NG:</p>
            <p class="m-0"><strong>May-ari:</strong> Elizabeth Angcanan (Maguyam, Silang, Cavite)</p>
            <p class="m-0"><strong>Nangungupahan:</strong> <%= user.first_name %> <%= user.last_name %></p>
            <p class="m-0"><strong>Inilaang Kwarto Unit:</strong> <%= application.roomRequested %></p>

            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 border-b pb-1">I. MGA TUNTUNIN AT KONDISYON</h4>
            <p class="m-0">1. Ang buwanang upa para sa nasabing unit ay nagkakahalaga ng tunay na <strong>₱<%= application.monthlyRent.toLocaleString() %></strong>.</p>
            <p class="m-0">2. Ang Nangungupahan ay sumasang-ayon na bayaran ang upa sa itinakdang takdang-araw buwan-buwan.</p>
            <p class="m-0">3. Ang kabuuang bilang ng mga residenteng mananatili sa loob ng unit ay hindi dapat lalaktaw sa itinakdang limitasyon na 4 na katao.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>